Program: Omnibus
Title: Sylvia Pankhurst
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p0376lwm
Last Broadcast Date: 04 May 1999
The life of militant suffragette Sylvia Pankhurst and her role as adviser to the Ethiopian Emperor, Haile Selassie. Contributors include her son Richard Pankhurst and there is an archive interview with Sylvia herself. Picture: Sylvia Pankhurst, Credit: Getty Images